 107:
 108: ### RCR-P0-001: Auth context trust boundary is not enforced
 109:
 110: - Severity: P0
 111: - Requirement IDs: `FR-009`, `AC-009`, `AC-E006`, `AC-E016`
 112: - Evidence:
 113:   - `src/audit-log/auth-context.ts:46-63` 直接从 `x-operator-id`、`x-tenant-id`、`x-role-codes`、`x-org-scope`、`x-request-id` 构造认证上下文。
 114:   - `src/audit-log/auth-context.ts:26-27` 将请求头中的 `EXPORT_ADMIN` 作为管理员判断。
 115:   - `src/task-api/service.ts:624-633` 管理员历史查询可不受租户过滤。
 116: - Risk: 能直连服务的调用方可伪造管理员或跨租户上下文，绕过任务可见性和下载权限。
 117: - Suggested next task id: `AUTH-CONTEXT-TRUST-BOUNDARY-001`
 118:
 119: ### RCR-P0-002: query data scope ignores operatorId, roleCodes, and registry dataScopeTemplate
 120:
 121: - Severity: P0
 122: - Requirement IDs: `FR-008`, `FR-009`, `AC-008`, `AC-009`
 123: - Evidence:
 124:   - `docs/product/prd-lite.md` 要求查询叠加 `tenantId`、`operatorId`、`roleCodes`、`orgScope` 数据范围约束。
 125:   - `src/query-executor/index.ts:352-364` 只构造 `tenantId + orgScope`。
 126:   - `src/query-executor/index.ts:393-405` 硬编码 `tenantId = ? AND orgId IN (...)`，未使用 registry `dataScopeTemplate`。
 127: - Risk: 同租户同组织内不同操作人或角色的数据隔离无法证明，可能导出越权数据。
 128: - Suggested next task id: `DATA-SCOPE-TEMPLATE-ENFORCE-001`
 129:
 130: ### RCR-P0-003: signed URL is not cryptographically signed and uses file retention expiry
 131:
 132: - Severity: P0
 133: - Requirement IDs: `FR-003`, `FR-009`, `AC-003`, `AC-009`
 134: - Evidence:
 135:   - `src/file-service/index.ts:117-120` 的 `createDownloadUrl` 只追加 `expiresAt` 查询参数，没有签名。
